sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant GH as GitHub
    participant CI as GitHub Actions
    participant App as NetworkBuster App

    Dev->>GH: Add OPENAI_API_KEY secret (via UI or CLI)
    GH->>CI: Secrets available to workflows
    CI->>CI: Validate secret (models endpoint)
    CI->>App: Start server and run E2E smoke test (/api/recycle/recommend)
    App-->>CI: Return recommendations (ok: true)
    CI-->>Dev: Report result (success/failure)
